ivardefs.name: adjudication_
ivardefs.desc: The adjudications results.

ivardefs.name: bodySite
ivardefs.desc: Physical service site on the patient (limb, tooth, etc).

ivardefs.name: careTeamLinkId_
ivardefs.desc: Careteam applicable for this service or product line.

ivardefs.name: category
ivardefs.desc: Health Care Service Type Codes  to identify the classification of service or benefits.

ivardefs.name: detail_
ivardefs.desc: Second tier of goods and services.

ivardefs.name: diagnosisLinkId_
ivardefs.desc: Diagnosis applicable for this service or product line.

ivardefs.name: encounter_
ivardefs.desc: A billed item may include goods or services provided in multiple encounters.

ivardefs.name: factor
ivardefs.desc: A real number that represents a multiplier used in determining the overall value of services delivered and/or goods received. The concept of a Factor allows for a discount or surcharge multiplier to be applied to a monetary amount.

ivardefs.name: informationLinkId_
ivardefs.desc: Exceptions, special conditions and supporting information pplicable for this service or product line.

ivardefs.name: modifier_
ivardefs.desc: Item typification or modifiers codes, eg for Oral whether the treatment is cosmetic or associated with TMJ, or for medical whether the treatment was outside the clinic or out of office hours.

ivardefs.name: net
ivardefs.desc: The quantity times the unit price for an addittional service or product or charge. For example, the formula: unit Quantity * unit Price (Cost per Point) * factor Number  * points = net Amount. Quantity, factor and points are assumed to be 1 if not supplie

ivardefs.name: noteNumber_
ivardefs.desc: A list of note references to the notes provided below.

ivardefs.name: procedureLinkId_
ivardefs.desc: Procedures applicable for this service or product line.

ivardefs.name: programCode_
ivardefs.desc: For programs which require reson codes for the inclusion, covering, of this billed item under the program or sub-program.

ivardefs.name: quantity
ivardefs.desc: The number of repetitions of a service or product.

ivardefs.name: revenue
ivardefs.desc: The type of reveneu or cost center providing the product and/or service.

ivardefs.name: sequence
ivardefs.desc: A service line number.

ivardefs.name: service
ivardefs.desc: If this is an actual service or product line, ie. not a Group, then use code to indicate the Professional Service or Product supplied (eg. CTP, HCPCS,USCLS,ICD10, NCPDP,DIN,ACHI,CCI). If a grouping item then use a group code to indicate the type of thing

ivardefs.name: subSite_
ivardefs.desc: A region or surface of the site, eg. limb region or tooth surface(s).

ivardefs.name: udi_
ivardefs.desc: List of Unique Device Identifiers associated with this line item.

ivardefs.name: unitPrice
ivardefs.desc: If the item is a node then this is the fee for the product or service, otherwise this is the total of the fees for the children of the group.

properties.desc: First tier of goods and services.
